        'benmarwick@gmail.com', role = 'ctb'))
Description: Utilities for converting unstructured electronic
        prescribing instructions into structured medication data.
        Extracts drug dose, units, daily dosing frequency and intervals
        from English-language prescriptions. Based on Karystianis et
        al. (2015) <doi:10.1186/s12911-016-0255-x>.
